text:
> Pennsylvania Cardinals rout Pirates, clinch 3rd straight NL Central title Pittsburgh Pirates starting pitcher Charlie Morton delivers in the first inning of a baseball game against the St. Louis Cardinals in Pittsburgh, Wednesday, Sept. 30, 2015.
